isit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20journey%20was%20far%20from%20easy.%20Early%20funding%20rejections%20were%20disheartening%2C%20and%20convincing%20companies%20to%20invest%20in%20land%20restoration%20proved%20challenging.%20Many%20felt%20the%20work%20required%20too%20much%20effort%20with%20little%20visible%20outcome%20in%20the%20short%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Vikrant%E2%80%99s%20determination%20never%20faltered.%20He%20continued%20approaching%20corporate%20allies%20and%20individuals%2C%20explaining%20why%20this%20effort%20mattered.%20Eventually%2C%20with%20support%20through%20CSR%20funds%20and%20personal%20contributions%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20gather%20the%20resources%20needed.%20In%20total%2C%20transforming%20the%20site%20cost%20around%20%E2%82%B910%20lakh%20%E2%80%94%20an%20amount%20that%20turned%20a%20barren%20wasteland%20into%20a%20thriving%20green%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20was%20profound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-1-1753705257.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Over%203%2C000%20trees%20now%20grow%20on%20the%20site%2C%20which%20has%20become%20a%20habitat%20for%20local%20wildlife%20and%20a%20recreational%20area%20for%20residents.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-1-1753705257.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-1-1753705257-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-1-1753705257-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.co