strong%3ESELCO%20Foundation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20develops%20decentralised%20renewable%20energy-based%20solutions.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20new%20way%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20weather%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Socratus%20began%20looking%20for%20a%20place%20to%20test%20its%20ideas%2C%20Odisha%20felt%20like%20the%20obvious%20choice.%20The%20state%20lives%20under%20the%20constant%20threat%20of%20cyclones%20and%20floods.%20Its%20landscapes%20%E2%80%94%20from%20dense%20forests%20to%20fragile%20coastlines%20%E2%80%94%20are%20among%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20to%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOdisha%20also%20had%20a%20strong%20base%20to%20build%20on.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20Indian%20state%20to%20adopt%20a%20comprehensive%20climate%20action%20plan%2C%20with%20systems%20stretching%20from%20the%20grassroots%20to%20the%20state%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20important%20are%20the%20people.%20Nearly%2023%20percent%20of%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20population%20belongs%20to%2064%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%20Twelve%20out%20of%20its%2030%20districts%20are%20tribal-dominated%2C%20home%20to%20communities%20living%20across%20forests%2C%20wetlands%2C%20farmlands%2C%20and%20coastal%20belts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20bring%20its%20philosophy%20to%20life%2C%20Socratus%20teamed%20up%20with%20organisations%20like%20Sambad%20and%20Bakul%20Foundation%20and%20launched%20the%20Climate%20Panchayat%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fimage10_11zon-1-1753883935-500x855.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20colourful%20maps%20of%20Odisha%20showing%20groundwater%2C%20temperature%2C%20and%20extreme%20weather%20trends.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22ht